Claudia Drake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claudia_Drake 0 Claudia Drake (January 30, 1918 – October 19, 1997) was an American actress and singer. She appeared in a number of B Movies in a mixture of leading and supporting roles. She starred in the 1945 film noir Detour.
